<refentry id="element.phone">
  <refnamediv>
    <refname>phone</refname>
    <refpurpose>A phone number</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>

  <refsynopsisdiv><title>Synopsis</title>
    <refsect2><title>Content Model</title>
      <synopsis><$CONTENT_MODEL$></synopsis>
    </refsect2>
    <refsect2><title>Attributes</title>
      <$ATTRIBUTES_TABLE$>
    </refsect2>
  </refsynopsisdiv>

  <refsect1><title>Description</title>
    <para>
      The <sgmltag class="element">phone</sgmltag> element contains a
      telephone number. The number is not required to be in a specific format;
      these are all valid phone numbers:

      <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
        <listitem><para>
          <literal><![CDATA[<phone>555-555-1212</phone>]]></literal>
        </para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>
          <literal><![CDATA[<phone>555.555.1212</phone>]]></literal>
        </para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>
          <literal><![CDATA[<phone>(555) 555-1212</phone>]]></literal>
        </para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>
          <literal><![CDATA[<phone>(555) 555-1212 x555</phone>]]></literal>
        </para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>
          <literal><![CDATA[<phone>(011) 47 8931-858128</phone>]]></literal>
        </para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>
          <literal><![CDATA[<phone>(011) 59-3331-8580</phone>]]></literal>
        </para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>
          <literal><![CDATA[<phone>Mobile: 555-1212</phone>]]></literal>
        </para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>
          <literal><![CDATA[<phone>Fax: 555-1212</phone>]]></literal>
        </para></listitem>
      </itemizedlist>

      The last two items on the list are the currently recommended method of
      identifying non-primary phone numbers. However alternatives to this
      method are being investegated by the &libarary.name; team. This will
      probably change in a future version.

    </para>

